00:01:47.790 --> 00:01:49.500
And snapping is
bewildering, because it's

00:01:49.500 --> 00:01:53.790
this unconscious aggressive
impulse triggered by something

00:01:53.790 --> 00:01:55.092
in the environment.

00:01:55.092 --> 00:01:56.050
